        And they drown.

35:37.870 --> 35:40.403
      (electric buzzing)

35:40.405 --> 35:42.772
         (weird music)

35:45.577 --> 35:48.311
        (deep rumbling)

35:58.824 --> 36:01.658
      (fiery crackling)

36:03.829 --> 36:06.730
      (heavy whooshing)

36:09.601 --> 36:12.369
         (air sucking)

36:37.930 --> 36:40.597
         (Max coughs)

36:50.375 --> 36:53.343
      (suspicious music)

36:57.616 --> 37:01.384
    - You could've drowned
    today, but you didn't.

