37:17.669 --> 37:19.703
         But you did.

37:19.705 --> 37:22.772
      You held on to see
      this thing through.

37:22.774 --> 37:24.307
     I respect that, Max.

37:24.977 --> 37:26.243
     I'm gonna let you in

