      (mysterious music)

37:37.990 --> 37:40.724
        (Edmund laughs)

37:43.295 --> 37:44.594
 - [Max] You're fucking crazy.

37:44.596 --> 37:46.963
         (misty music)

37:48.300 --> 37:49.032
         - Come again?

37:50.669 --> 37:51.768
         - I'm sorry.

37:53.572 --> 37:54.838
I'm pretty rattled after today.

37:54.840 --> 37:56.373
 Drowning's pretty exhausting.

